# Architecture & documentation context

This repo is a **modular monolith** (DDD bounded contexts): backend `app/api/modules/`, frontend `app/web/src/features/`, mirroring BC names. **State isolation is critical**—no shared DB tables, no cross-BC foreign keys, no cross-BC session imports. BCs communicate via Protocols and HTTP clients only.

APIs are **dual-purpose**: design for both the web UI and AI/agent tool calls.

