## Invariants (short)

- Namespace packages only — **no** `__init__.py`
- **Pydantic** for DTOs, config, external types
- **No ORM in services**; **no repositories in routers** (services only)
- BC-prefixed table names; **StrEnum** for status/role/type fields
- **No cross-BC DB access** — use Protocols or HTTP clients
- One transaction per write: `with session.begin()`

Session workflow, issue tracking (`bd`), and push protocol live in **`CLAUDE.md`** at the repo root. Principles: **`docs/PRINCIPLES.md`**. Run the stack: **`CONTRIBUTING.md`**. Module tree: **`docs/patterns/backend/module-design.md`**. Testing: **`docs/patterns/backend/testing.md`**.
